            "item_id": 802839659,
            "art_id": 3418244118,
            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "03 Mar 2016 21:52:29 GMT",
            "about": "'...Moving yet not moving, thrown by what hand, timelessly circling, creating time.'\nThe Dispossessed - Ursula K. LeGuin\n'They didn't know that the future was on their side, that the future was impossible without them. They didn't know that in a world belonging to the terrible ghosts of the past, they were the only manifestation of the future...'\nHard to Be a God - Arkady and Boris Strugatsky\n'But into that tangle, just as crucial, went the smell of the cover, the color and cream resistance of the pages, the week in which I read any given epic, the friends for whom I synopsized, the bed, the lamp, the room where I read.'\nGalatea 2.2 - Richard Powers",
            "credits": "released March 3, 2016\nrecorded in east somerville, ma.\nlate winter, 2016.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a3418244118_0",
