            "about": "pushing and pulling, reaching out though the crowds and the noise, pounding the pavements, marking time, pacing, plotting, walking and rewalking the same streets, roads, circles, paths, sidewalks, parking lots, vacant lots, underpasses, overpasses, tracks, cracks, concrete, asphalt, gravel, puddles, grass, leaves, dust, dirt, mud, shadows, snow...\nhopes, memories, observations...",
            "credits": "released February 29, 2020\nrecorded in late january and early february, 2020\neast somerville, ma",
