            "item_id": 3162947897,
            "art_id": 856203574,
            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "01 Feb 2026 00:01:14 GMT",
            "about": "The lightning season here is late July, early August. Storms appear late afternoon. You see them way off in the mountains, one, then another, sort of crawling down the sky, too far off to be audible yet. A storm may fade and die long before it gets here, and another storm approaches, and then another begins to build somewhere else.\nDon DeLillo - Love-Lies-Bleeding",
            "credits": "released February 1, 2026\nrecorded in wanskuck, providence, ri\ndecember 2025",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a0856203574_0",
